OL,3,CHealth secretary promises to meet with
OL,4,CDES drug scandal victims
OL,6,FSpeaking in the House of Commons, the
OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said he
OL,8,Fwould meet with victims exposed to the
OL,9,Fdrug DES, which was prescribed on the
OL,10,FNHS for decades.
OL,12,FITV News Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,13,FSarah Corker and Senior Producer
OL,14,FLottie Kilraine report
OL,16,FThe health secretary has promised to
OL,17,Fmeet with women affected by the
OL,18,Fpregnancy drug DES to hear of their
OL,19,Fexperiences first-hand, after a year-
OL,20,Flong ITV News investigation exposed
OL,21,Fthe scale of the medical scandal.
