OL,3,CHealth secretary promises to meet with
OL,4,CDES drug scandal victims
OL,6,FStilbestrol, commonly known as DES,
OL,7,Fwas a synthetic hormone prescribed to
OL,8,Fan estimated 300,000 women on the NHS
OL,9,Fbetween the late 1930s and 1980s to
OL,10,Ftreat several issues, including
OL,11,Fmiscarriage, until it was linked to
OL,12,Frare cancers and infertility in the
OL,13,Fchildren of those who took it.
OL,15,FFor months, ITV News has been
OL,16,Fhighlighting the failures of the
OL,17,Fhealth authorities to act on safety
OL,18,Fwarnings about the drug's sinister
OL,19,Fside effects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
