OL,3,CHealth secretary promises to meet with
OL,4,CDES drug scandal victims
OL,6,FThis significant development comes
OL,7,Fjust weeks after Wes Streeting
OL,8,Fadmitted that "the state got this
OL,9,Fwrong" and apologised on behalf of the
OL,10,Fgovernment to victims.
OL,12,FAddressing him in Parliament, Layla
OL,13,FMoran MP, who chairs the select
OL,14,Fcommittee responsible for scrutinising
OL,15,Fthe Department of Health, pressed
OL,16,FStreeting on what action he is taking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
