OL,3,CHealth secretary promises to meet with
OL,4,CDES drug scandal victims
OL,6,F"Two weeks ago, the secretary of state
OL,7,Fmade an apology to victims, but they
OL,8,Frightly want more than 'sorry' and
OL,9,Fthey point out that the screening
OL,10,Fprogramme is insufficient," she said.
OL,12,F"So, will the secretary of state meet
OL,13,Fwith me, campaigners, and victims to
OL,14,Funderstand how this was allowed to
OL,15,Fhappen, who is going to be held
OL,16,Faccountable and how they can go about
OL,17,Fgetting compensation for this
OL,18,Fegregious scandal?"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
