OL,6,FThe health secretary responded by
OL,7,Freiterating his apology to victims for
OL,8,Fthe "failure that occurred and the
OL,9,Fharm that has arisen as a result" and
OL,10,Fsaid he would be "delighted" to attend
OL,11,Fa meeting.
OL,13,FStreeting also thanked the more than
OL,14,F400 survivors who have formed DES
OL,15,FJustice UK following ITV News'
OL,16,Freporting, adding that campaigners had
OL,17,Fdone "a magnificent job raising public
OL,18,Fawareness".
