OL,3,CHealth secretary promises to meet with
OL,4,CDES drug scandal victims
OL,6,FAs well as a meeting with the health
OL,7,Fsecretary, victims and their families
OL,8,Fare calling for a full statutory
OL,9,Fpublic inquiry, with clear
OL,10,Frecommendations followed by swift
OL,11,Factions.
OL,13,FThey also want an information campaign
OL,14,Fto ensure healthcare professionals are
OL,15,Faware of DES, medical research into
OL,16,Fthe long-term, intergenerational
OL,17,Feffects of the drug, targeted
OL,18,Fscreening for cancers and fertility
OL,19,Fissues and a compensation fund.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
