OL,3,CHealth secretary promises to meet with
OL,4,CDES drug scandal victims
OL,6,FThe women who believe they were
OL,7,Fexposed to DES tell ITV News about
OL,8,Fhealth problems they fear may be
OL,9,Flinked to the drug. This is their
OL,10,Fstory in their own words.
OL,12,FDES, originally called
OL,13,FDiethylstilboestrol, is a synthetic
OL,14,Foestrogen invented in Britain in 1939.
OL,15,FResearch suggests pregnant women who
OL,16,Ftook DES may have a 30% higher risk of
OL,17,Fbreast cancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
