OL,4,CDES drug scandal victims
OL,6,FTheir daughters, known as DES
OL,7,Fdaughters, exposed in the womb, are at
OL,8,Fan increased risk of clear cell cancer
OL,9,Fof the cervix and vagina, which is not
OL,10,Fpicked up by routine screening.
OL,12,FIn September, the medicines regulator
OL,13,F(MHRA) admitted it had misled the
OL,14,Fpublic for up to 25 years about when
OL,15,Fthe drug was withdrawn and issued an
OL,16,Fapology last month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
