OL,3,CHealth secretary promises to meet with
OL,4,CDES drug scandal victims
OL,6,FThe MHRA had falsely claimed that
OL,7,Fdoctors were advised to stop using the
OL,8,Fdrug for use in pre-menopausal women
OL,9,Fin 1973, a statement that our
OL,10,Freporting has exposed as inaccurate.
OL,12,FThe regulator then admitted that
OL,13,Finformation was incorrect, and the
OL,14,Fdrug was not stopped for use in
OL,15,Fpregnancy until the 1980s, more than a
OL,16,Fdecade after cancer risks were known.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
