OL,3,CHealth secretary promises to meet with
OL,4,CDES drug scandal victims
OL,6,FThe health secretary's sustained
OL,7,Facknowledgement this week of the harm
OL,8,Fcaused and his pledge to meet with
OL,9,Fcampaigners is a promising
OL,10,Fdevelopment, but he has been careful
OL,11,Fwith his wording throughout to not
OL,12,Faccept liability.
OL,14,FFor now, the victims of DES and their
OL,15,Ffamilies, who have waited so long for
OL,16,Ftheir voices to be heard, will
OL,17,Fcontinue their fight but with a close
OL,18,Feye on Streeting to see if his words
OL,19,Fwill translate into actions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
